 sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.4367918491363525;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-right: 42.933013916015625pt;text-indent: -17.439002990722656pt;margin-top:3.44439697265625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.439002990722656pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● No hosting of proxy servers, VPN exit nodes, or anonymization tools unless</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">approved.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.5459976196289062pt;margin-top:32.302001953125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">6. Intellectual Property Compliance</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:2.873606014251709;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-right: 8.933319091796875pt;margin-top:3.6387939453125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Content hosted must not violate copyrights, trademarks, patents, or other IP rights.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● DMCA or equivalent legal notices must be respected.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.5459976196289062pt;margin-top:19.131195068359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">7. Resource Abuse</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.436814022064209;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-right: 11.418365478515625pt;text-indent: -17.439002990722656pt;margin-top:3.638824462890625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.439002990722656pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Excessive CPU, RAM, bandwidth, or disk usage that impacts server stability is not</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">allowed.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:16.614288330078125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Long-running scripts or cron jobs must be optimized.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:18.785552978515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Fair usage policy applies to all shared resources.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.5329971313476562pt;margin-top:53.158111572265625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">8. Consequences of Violation</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:3.639068603515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Warning or temporary suspension</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:18.785308837890625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Permanent service termination</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:18.785308837890625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Blacklisting of domain/IP</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:18.785308837890625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● Reporting to legal authorities (for illegal activities)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4160003662109375pt;margin-top:34.472320556640625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">9. Provider Rights</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:3.6390609741210938pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● The hosting provider may update the AUP at any time.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:18.785316467285156pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● The provider may take immediate action if services threaten security, stability, or</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 36.714996337890625pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">reputation.</span></p><div><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><br></span></div></span>',7,'annish','customer',1,0,'2026-01-08 07:51:49','2026-01-08 15:41:09',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL),(7,'Google Workspace Email Sending Limits','google-workspace-email-sending-limits-1767858930372','<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please be advised that all email accounts within our Google Workspace environment are subject to strict sending limits enforced by Google to maintain service health and prevent abuse.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">You can find the definitive and most up-to-date policy directly on the official Google Workspace Admin Help page:</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://support.google.com/a/answer/166852\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.google.com/a/answer/166852&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767945258890000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2z6QomD2vQbbWBv3F5ELaD\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Official Google Workspace Sending Limits</a></b></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Key Limits to Note</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">For a standard paid account, the primary limits enforced over a rolling 24-hour period are:</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Maximum Messages Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>2,000</b></p></li><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Total Recipients Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>10,000</b></p></li></span><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Recipients in a Single Message (Web/Mobile):</b>&nbsp;<b>2,000</b></p></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;Exceeding any of these limits will result in a temporary suspension of your sending ability for up to 24 hours. For high-volume or marketing campaigns, we strongly recommend using a dedicated third-party Email Service Provider (ESP) instead of your Google Workspace mailbox.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p></span>',7,'annish','customer',1,0,'2026-01-08 07:55:30','2026-01-08 07:55:39',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL),(8,'Microsoft 365 Email Sending Limits','microsoft-365-email-sending-limits-1767859022326','<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please be advised that all email accounts within our Microsoft 365 Exchange Online environment are subject to strict sending limits enforced by Microsoft.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">You can find the definitive and most up-to-date policy on the official Microsoft documentation:&nbsp;<b><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office365/servicedescriptions/exchange-online-service-description/exchange-online-limits\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office365/servicedescriptions/exchange-online-service-description/exchange-online-limits&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767945369778000&amp;usg=AOvVaw30wqLLLAOJq1hWvy9tshSL\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Exchange Online Limits</a><br></b><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\"></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Key Limits to Note</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">The primary limits are enforced over a&nbsp;<b>rolling 24-hour period</b>.</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Total Recipients Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>10,000</b></p></li></span><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Recipients in a Single Message:</b>&nbsp;<b>500</b></p></li></ul><h4 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Hourly/Rate Restriction (Messages Per Minute)</h4><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Message Rate Limit:</b>&nbsp;A maximum of&nbsp;<b>30 messages per minute</b>&nbsp;can be sent when using SMTP client submission (e.g., desktop mail clients or automated systems). Attempting to send messages faster than this rate will result in the mail being temporarily throttled or rejected.</p></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;For high-volume or marketing campaigns, please use a dedicated third-party Email Service Provider (ESP) to ensure uninterrupted service for your primary business email.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p></span>',7,'annish','both',1,0,'2026-01-08 07:57:02','2026-01-08 15:34:18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL),(9,'This is what i should do','this-is-what-i-should-do-1767886904182','<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\"><br><br>Use this as a reference point',NULL,'admin','both',1,0,'2026-01-08 15:41:44','2026-01-08 15:41:56',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL);
