ition: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.4160003662109375pt;margin-top:34.472320556640625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">9. Provider Rights</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 18.957000732421875pt;margin-top:3.6390609741210938pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● The hosting provider may update the AUP at any time.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:18.785316467285156pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">● The provider may take immediate action if services threaten security, stability, or</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 36.714996337890625pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">reputation.</span></p><div><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><br></span></div></span>','annish','2026-01-08 07:52:39'),(13,7,1,'<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please be advised that all email accounts within our Google Workspace environment are subject to strict sending limits enforced by Google to maintain service health and prevent abuse.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">You can find the definitive and most up-to-date policy directly on the official Google Workspace Admin Help page:</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://support.google.com/a/answer/166852\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.google.com/a/answer/166852&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767945258890000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2z6QomD2vQbbWBv3F5ELaD\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Official Google Workspace Sending Limits</a></b></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Key Limits to Note</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">For a standard paid account, the primary limits enforced over a rolling 24-hour period are:</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Maximum Messages Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>2,000</b></p></li><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Total Recipients Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>10,000</b></p></li></span><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Recipients in a Single Message (Web/Mobile):</b>&nbsp;<b>2,000</b></p></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;Exceeding any of these limits will result in a temporary suspension of your sending ability for up to 24 hours. For high-volume or marketing campaigns, we strongly recommend using a dedicated third-party Email Service Provider (ESP) instead of your Google Workspace mailbox.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p></span>','annish','2026-01-08 07:55:30'),(14,7,2,'<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please be advised that all email accounts within our Google Workspace environment are subject to strict sending limits enforced by Google to maintain service health and prevent abuse.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">You can find the definitive and most up-to-date policy directly on the official Google Workspace Admin Help page:</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://support.google.com/a/answer/166852\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.google.com/a/answer/166852&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767945258890000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2z6QomD2vQbbWBv3F5ELaD\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Official Google Workspace Sending Limits</a></b></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Key Limits to Note</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">For a standard paid account, the primary limits enforced over a rolling 24-hour period are:</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Maximum Messages Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>2,000</b></p></li><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Total Recipients Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>10,000</b></p></li></span><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Recipients in a Single Message (Web/Mobile):</b>&nbsp;<b>2,000</b></p></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;Exceeding any of these limits will result in a temporary suspension of your sending ability for up to 24 hours. For high-volume or marketing campaigns, we strongly recommend using a dedicated third-party Email Service Provider (ESP) instead of your Google Workspace mailbox.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p></span>','annish','2026-01-08 07:55:39'),(15,8,1,'<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please be advised that all email accounts within our Microsoft 365 Exchange Online environment are subject to strict sending limits enforced by Microsoft.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">You can find the definitive and most up-to-date policy on the official Microsoft documentation:&nbsp;<b><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office365/servicedescriptions/exchange-online-service-description/exchange-online-limits\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office365/servicedescriptions/exchange-online-service-description/exchange-online-limits&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767945369778000&amp;usg=AOvVaw30wqLLLAOJq1hWvy9tshSL\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Exchange Online Limits</a></b></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Key Limits to Note</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">The primary limits are enforced over a&nbsp;<b>rolling 24-hour period</b>.</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Total Recipients Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>10,000</b></p></li></span><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Recipients in a Single Message:</b>&nbsp;<b>500</b></p></li></ul><h4 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Hourly/Rate Restriction (Messages Per Minute)</h4><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Message Rate Limit:</b>&nbsp;A maximum of&nbsp;<b>30 messages per minute</b>&nbsp;can be sent when using SMTP client submission (e.g., desktop mail clients or automated systems). Attempting to send messages faster than this rate will result in the mail being temporarily throttled or rejected.</p></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;For high-volume or marketing campaigns, please use a dedicated third-party Email Service Provider (ESP) to ensure uninterrupted service for your primary business email.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p></span>','annish','2026-01-08 07:57:02'),(16,8,2,'<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please be advised that all email accounts within our Microsoft 365 Exchange Online environment are subject to strict sending limits enforced by Microsoft.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">You can find the definitive and most up-to-date policy on the official Microsoft documentation:&nbsp;<b><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office365/servicedescriptions/exchange-online-service-description/exchange-online-limits\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office365/servicedescriptions/exchange-online-service-description/exchange-online-limits&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767945369778000&amp;usg=AOvVaw30wqLLLAOJq1hWvy9tshSL\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Exchange Online Limits</a><br></b><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\"></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Key Limits to Note</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">The primary limits are enforced over a&nbsp;<b>rolling 24-hour period</b>.</p><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Total Recipients Per Day:</b>&nbsp;<b>10,000</b></p></li></span><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Recipients in a Single Message:</b>&nbsp;<b>500</b></p></li></ul><h4 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Hourly/Rate Restriction (Messages Per Minute)</h4><ul style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><b>Message Rate Limit:</b>&nbsp;A maximum of&nbsp;<b>30 messages per minute</b>&nbsp;can be sent when using SMTP client submission (e.g., desktop mail clients or automated systems). Attempting to send messages faster than this rate will result in the mail being temporarily throttled or rejected.</p></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;For high-volume or marketing campaigns, please use a dedicated third-party Email Service Provider (ESP) to ensure uninterrupted service for your primary business email.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p></span>','admin','2026-01-08 15:34:18'),(17,6,3,'<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e1389ba2-7fff-7ee2-7614-54d5cc3aec7e\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.3218586921691895;margin-right: 5.7431640625pt;text-indent: -1.240997314453125pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.240997314453125pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Acceptable Use Policy (AUP) – Server Hosting &amp; Email</span><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Hosting Packages</span><span style=\"font-size: 17pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 1.144500732421875pt;margin-top:13.318359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">1.Email storage cannot exceed 50% of your hosting disk space</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.30449676513671875pt;margin-top:11.82049560546875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2.Email storage must not exceed 10 GB, even if within the 50% limit</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.44100189208984375pt;margin-top:11.82049560546875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">3.Mailboxes cannot be used as long-term storage or archive dumping</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.13649749755859375pt;margin-top:11.82049560546875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">4.Zero tolerance for spam — no unsolicited bulk or commercial emails</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.44100189208984375pt;margin-top:11.82049560546875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">5.Any email activity must comply with the U.S. CAN-SPAM Act</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.3990020751953125pt;margin-top:11.82049560546875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">6.You must not engage in any illegal or harmful email activity</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:2.291842317581177;margin-left: 0.4304962158203125pt;margin-right: 76.41464233398438pt;text-indent: 0.0630035400390625pt;margin-top:11.82049560546875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">7.Hosting is strictly for website files, active emails, and site content Not allowed:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">8.Storing large media, backups, or files unrelated to your website</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.44100189208984375pt;margin-top:2.266845703125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">9.Using hosting as offsite storage, gaming servers, or FTP storage</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:35.894439697265625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Account limits must be followed:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.7770004272460938pt;margin-top:11.820465087890625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Max 100,000 files (inodes)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: 